{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-template-js","path":"/posts/indent-rainbow","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"7fe28e51-35e6-5ae6-ab0f-205cb8227bf4","html":"<p>Indent rainbow is a simple extension that makes indentation more readable by colorizing each tab indentation.</p>\n<p>Just head to <a href=\"https://marketplace.visualstudio.com/items?itemName=oderwat.indent-rainbow\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">VS Code Marketplace</a> and install the extension. Period.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 924px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/79cde3913df13754ec85bc0f6b36582f/9a1cf/indent.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 57.50000000000001%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/79cde3913df13754ec85bc0f6b36582f/8ac56/indent.webp 240w,\n/static/79cde3913df13754ec85bc0f6b36582f/d3be9/indent.webp 480w,\n/static/79cde3913df13754ec85bc0f6b36582f/c3b05/indent.webp 924w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 924px) 100vw, 924px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/79cde3913df13754ec85bc0f6b36582f/8ff5a/indent.png 240w,\n/static/79cde3913df13754ec85bc0f6b36582f/e85cb/indent.png 480w,\n/static/79cde3913df13754ec85bc0f6b36582f/9a1cf/indent.png 924w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 924px) 100vw, 924px\"\n          type=\"image/png\"\n        />\n        <img\n          class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n          src=\"/static/79cde3913df13754ec85bc0f6b36582f/9a1cf/indent.png\"\n          alt=\"Screenshot\"\n          title=\"Screenshot\"\n          loading=\"lazy\"\n          style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        />\n      </picture>\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>This extension colorizes the indentation in front of your text alternating four different colors on each step. Some may find it helpful in writing code for Nim or Python.\nBy default it comes with a ‚Äúrainbow‚Äù of colors, but if you prefer something more subtle like me, simply past the following configuration into your User Settings. Refer its documentation <a href=\"https://marketplace.visualstudio.com/items?itemName=oderwat.indent-rainbow\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">here</a></p>\n<p>These colors work great with the default VSCode theme and seamlessly blend in the default VSCode color scheme.</p>\n<p>Official Repo: <a href=\"https://github.com/oderwat/vscode-indent-rainbow\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">Indent-Rainbow</a></p>\n<hr>","fields":{"slug":"/posts/indent-rainbow","tagSlugs":null},"frontmatter":{"date":"2019-08-17T18:05:00.738Z","description":"Extension to highlight and group indented code in different color ","tags":null,"title":"Visual Indentation equals Readable Code üåà","socialImage":null}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/posts/indent-rainbow"}}}